items.text: Spicy garlic lemon chicken - you have to try it & get extra garlic sauce - Yum!

formattedAddress: 3332 S Bristol St (at Alton Ave)

items.text: See Erika! Always entertaining & fun. You won't be disappointed!
White Roll is my favorite & Spicy Tuna on crispy rice with a side of spicy mayo...mmmm! Can't go wrong with a place that gives out saki on the house ;)
Try the albacore supreme roll - Yum!
7th floor facing the ocean - spectacular view!
Get the Wings and Irish Nachos!  And say Hi to my dad - his pic is hanging in the side room - the old guy with the beard! Have a drink with him :)
See Erika - she fun and amazing! :)
